data.description: Discover this charming Chandler home, a gem of potential and functionality. Pergo flooring throughout this 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home ensures easy upkeep.  The versatile layout offers a separate living room and dinning area. An Arizona room perfect for relaxing without the heat. The backyard boasts a mature pecan tree, a tangelo tree,16 x 8 storage shed, and a backyard cottage/teenage game room  with electricity.  The oversized 2 car garage has cabinets and a separate tool storage room with entry from backyard as well.  The home is location is just over 2 miles from the loop 101, while still maintaining its charm in a quaint neighborhood.  Whether you're seeking a haven or a place to grow come view this home today.
